{"tid":1424443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隨著抗爭升級, 抗爭者唔只gear 升級, 心理質素都要升級","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:04:18.000Z","uid":196536,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02b7cd5e99ddc1474ac3a0a2e3f3eeb7594c3149","tid":1424443,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:53:23.000Z","msg":"小弟想講下發夢果陣以及做冷氣軍師果陣眼中所見所感, 希望各位巴絲比D意見, 會盡量簡短<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講, 小弟對抗爭者的建議係: 公關(PR), 警戒(ALERTNESS), 冷靜(CALM), 觀察(OBSERVATION) <br />\n記住<span style=\"color: red;\">PACO</span>就得啦<br />\n<strong>公關</strong><br />\n做人冇公關, 食屎架啦. 呢場抗爭香港人面對的敵人無比強大, 實在可以少一個敵人就少一個敵人.<br />\n希望任何情況下以不樹敵為大前提, 但絕非任人凌辱, 可以的話盡量對反對人士解釋抗爭初心, 抗爭者ge招牌大家有份省靚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>警戒</strong><br />\n面對越黎越全方位ge監控, 加上我地在明對家在暗, 你永遠唔知幾時上面掉個樽落黎, 或者暗角殺出一堆白衫軍. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發夢見到好多做炸兩ge廢中廢老, 輕則口沒遮攔, 重則設下陷阱等機會影抗爭者失控畫面加以渲染, 更甚者可能係有精神病, 要做好萬全準備應付突發事故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>冷靜</strong><br />\n越來越多po話勇武上頭, 講明先我係掉核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 不過手足千其唔好意氣用事, 三思而後行大有助益. 如身邊有同伴有失控跡象, 記得提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>觀察</strong><br />\n唔好低估發夢風險, 多D留意身邊有冇人要幫手, 發夢見到好多人係度鳩坐掃電話, 我真係覺得香港人危機意識太低. 時刻注意四周環境, 例如cam, 記者, 附近有冇可疑人物等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n四樣野知易行難, 歡迎討論分享<br />\n香港人, 共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"2161d91886a11bfe810eb7b88d2a37b5a3021ace","tid":1424443,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d302361a83a18f7113a8e7da6466cfecd1fd3b05","tid":1424443,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:27:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f91a2edc94d5228e1c8e9fb65ac804f7201effc3","tid":1424443,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:16:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76b702a5f93cde22aec3a395cf4c700254089d90","tid":1424443,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae1fe788d67b991e0ebc848b666d9f6a7ac9dfe1","tid":1424443,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"509cac9baabb50e3815c0352403ab51681e2b51f","tid":1424443,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3b25551bc9e04e399e029283ec1a8af4543f42e","tid":1424443,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}